9.4 DUIM-Frames Module

<property-page>

Open instantiable class

Summary

The class of property pages.

Superclasses

<page>

Init-keywords

None.

Library

duim-frames

Module

duim-frames

Description

The class of property pages. These are pages that can be displayed in an instance of <property-frame>.

Figure 9.4 A property page

Internally, this class maps into the Windows property page control.

Operations

None.
